How to use:
1. Input the formal code or Open from a file
2. Click the magic button and wait for the magic ( you don't have to wait )
3. Click start to run the code, a terminal screen will pop up
4. Right mouse click in terminal screen ( paste )
*If you by mistake copied something else, click the "Copy Function code" and right click again
